This torrent is horrible and almost a scam.. The original 16x9 aspect ratio has been destroyed by the encoder through black stripes added at the top and bottom, thus removing a lots of movie details.
The encoder probably did this to achieve a small file size because encoding black bars needs almost no bitrate at all.
So beware, small size has been achieved at the expense of movie integrity, even if the actual quality is decent.
